snippet.title: Warframe | The Deadlock Protocol - Corpus Remaster
snippet.description:
Explore a brand new Warframe Quest on a totally remastered Corpus fleet in The Deadlock Protocol! Available Now on PC.

Find out more about our plans for The Deadlock Protocol in Community and Live Ops Director Rebecca Ford's interview with IGN: https://www.ign.com/articles/warframe-corpus-reimagined-deadlock-protocol-update-remaster
